\c 11
\s UJoshuwa unqoba ilizwe lonke
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi lapho uJabini\x + Hlu. 4.2.\x* inkosi yeHazori\x + 12.19. 15.23. 19.36. Hlu. 4.2.\x* e\add ku\add*zwa, wathumela kuJobabi\x + 10.3.\x* inkosi yeMadoni\x + 12.19.\x*, lenkosini yeShimironi\x + 12.20. 19.15.\x*, lenkosini yeAkishafi\x + 12.20. 19.25.\x*,
\v 2 lemakhosini ayengenyakatho ezintabeni, lemagcekeni, eningizimu kweKinerothi\x + 12.3. 13.27. 19.35. Nani 34.11.\x*, lesihotsheni, lemaqaqeni eDori entshonalanga\x + 12.23; 17.11. 1 Kho. 4.11. Hlu. 1.27.\x*,
\v 3 amaKhanani empumalanga lentshonalanga, lamaAmori lamaHethi lamaPerizi lamaJebusi entabeni\x + 15.63.\x*, lamaHivi\x + Hlu. 3.3. 2 Sam. 24.7.\x* ngaphansi kweHermoni\x + Dute. 3.9.\x* elizweni leMizipa\x + 11.8. Gen. 31.49.13.26? Hlu. 10.17. 11.11,29,34. Josh. 15.38; 18.26.\x*.
\v 4 Asephuma, wona lawo wonke amabutho awo kanye lawo, abantu abanengi, njengetshebetshebe elisekhunjini lolwandle ngobunengi, lamabhiza lenqola okunengi kakhulu\x + Gen. 22.17. 32.12. Hlu. 7.12. 1 Sam. 13.5.\x*.
\v 5 Wonke lamakhosi asehlangana, eza amisa inkamba ndawonye emanzini eMeroma, ukulwa emelene loIsrayeli.
\p
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuJoshuwa: Ungesabi ngenxa yabo, ngoba kusasa phose ngalesisikhathi ngizawanikela wonke esebulewe phambi kukaIsrayeli\x + 10.8.\x*; uzaquma imisipha yamabhiza awo\x + 9. 2 Sam. 8.4. 1 Lan. 18.4. Gen. 49.6.\x*, utshise inqola zawo ngomlilo\x + Dute. 20.1. Josh. 17.16,18. Hlu. 1.19. 4.3.\x*.
\v 7 UJoshuwa wasesiza, labo bonke abantu bempi kanye laye, bemelene lawo emanzini eMeroma bawajuma\x + 10.9.\x*, bawadumela.
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiwanikela esandleni sikaIsrayeli, owawatshaya waxotshana lawo kwaze kwaba seSidoni enkulu, kwaze kwaba seMisirefothi-Mayimi, kwaze kwaba sesihotsheni seMizipa empumalanga\x + 11.3.\x*. Bawatshaya, kabaze batshiya insali kubo.
\v 9 UJoshuwa wasesenza kiwo njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuye; waquma imisipha yamabhiza awo, watshisa inqola zawo ngomlilo\x + 11.6.\x*.
\p
\v 10 UJoshuwa wasebuya ngalesosikhathi, wathumba iHazori, watshaya inkosi yayo ngenkemba. Ngoba kuqala iHazori yayiyinhloko yayo yonke leyomibuso.
\v 11 Batshaya yonke imiphefumulo eyayikiyo ngobukhali benkemba, bayitshabalalisa; kakusalanga lokukodwa okuphefumulayo; wasetshisa iHazori ngomlilo.
\v 12 Yonke-ke imizi yalawomakhosi lamakhosi ayo wonke uJoshuwa wakuthumba, wakutshaya ngobukhali benkemba, wakutshabalalisa, njengokulaya kukaMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\x + Dute. 20.16,17.\x*\nd*.
\v 13 Kuphela imizi yonke eyayimi emadundulwini ayo uIsrayeli kayitshisanga, ngaphandle kweHazori kuphela uJoshuwa ayitshisayo.
\v 14 Layo yonke impango yalimizi lezifuyo abantwana bakoIsrayeli baziphangela. Kuphela bonke abantu babatshaya ngobukhali benkemba baze babachitha; kabatshiyanga loyedwa ophefumulayo.
\p
\v 15 Njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimlayile uMozisi inceku yayo\x + Eks. 34.11,12.\x*, ngokunjalo uMozisi wamlaya uJoshuwa\x + Dute. 7.2.\x*, langokunjalo uJoshuwa wakwenza; kasusanga lutho kukho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakulaya uMozisi\x + 1.7.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho uJoshuwa walithatha lelolizwe lonke, izintaba, leningizimu yonke\x + 12.8.\x*, lelizwe lonke leGosheni, lesihotsha, lamagceke\x + 10.41. 15.51.\x*, lentaba zakoIsrayeli, lesigodi sakhe\x + 11.21.\x*,
\v 17 kusukela entabeni yeHalaki\x + 12.7.\x* eyenyukela eSeyiri\x + Gen. 14.6. 32.3. 36.8,9. Dute. 2.1,4,5. 33.2.\x*, kuze kube seBhali-Gadi esihotsheni seLebhanoni\x + 12.7. 13.5.\x* ngaphansi kwentaba yeHermoni\x + Dute. 3.9.\x*. Wawathumba wonke amakhosi abo, wawatshaya wawabulala.
\v 18 UJoshuwa wayilwa-ke impi insuku ezinengi lawo wonke lawomakhosi.
\v 19 Kakubanga lamuzi owenza ukuthula labantwana bakoIsrayeli ngaphandle kwamaHivi abahlali beGibeyoni\x + 9.3,7.\x*; bayithatha yonke ngempi.
\v 20 Ngoba kwakuvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ukwenza lukhuni inhliziyo zabo ukuze bahlangabezane loIsrayeli empini, ukuze abatshabalalise\x + Dute. 2.30. Hlu. 14.4. 1 Sam. 2.25. 1 Kho. 12.15. 2 Lan. 10.15. 22.7. 25.20. Roma 9.18. Eks. 7.13.\x*, ukuze bangazuzi umusa, kodwa ukuze ababhubhise, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi\x + Dute. 20.16,17.\x*.
\p
\v 21 UJoshuwa wasesiza ngalesosikhathi, waquma amaAnaki asuke ezintabeni\x + Nani 13.22.\x*, eHebroni\x + 10.3.\x*, eDebiri\x + 10.38.\x*, eAnabi, lentabeni zonke zakoJuda, lakuzo zonke intaba zakoIsrayeli; uJoshuwa wawatshabalalisa lemizi yawo.
\v 22 Kakusalanga amaAnaki elizweni labantwana bakoIsrayeli; kuphela eGaza\x + 15.47.\x*, eGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*, leAshidodi, asala\x + 1 Sam. 5.1.\x*.
\v 23 UJoshuwa wasethatha ilizwe lonke njengakho konke iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakukhuluma kuMozisi\x + Nani 34.2.\x*. UJoshuwa waselinika laba yilifa kuIsrayeli\x + Nani 26.53. 14.1-19,51.\x*, njengokwehlukaniswa kwabo ngezizwe zabo\x + 12.7. 18.10.\x*. Ilizwe laseliphumula empini\x + 14.15; 21.44; 22.4; 23.1; Hlu.3.11.\x*.
